  <verse number="15" style="v" />See that no one pay back evil for evil to anyone. Instead, pursue what is good for one another and for all.

  <verse number="16" style="v" />Rejoice always.

  <verse number="17" style="v" />Pray without ceasing.

  <verse number="18" style="v" />In everything give thanks. For this is the will of God in Christ Jesus for you.
